<T>__{dissolve to:}
<A>__{treves and merrick coming down the stairs. merrick is calm now. they go into the sitting room, where anne is just setting the tea tray out. treves ushers merrick to a highbacked sofa and sits him down. merrick is very shy of anne. treves and anne sit on the other side of the table.}
<C>__{anne}
<D>__{mr. merrick, sugar?}
<C>__{merrick}
<D>__{yes please, two.}
<C>__{anne}
<D>__{one or two?}
<C>__{merrick}
<D>__{two, please.}
<A>__{anne serves the tea.}
<C>__{treves}
<D>__{john loves the house.}
<C>__{anne}
<D>__{do you?}
