<D>__{yes, we do have a lot of room. but you should see the place on weekends, when i see patients here. sometimes there are so many, we have to set them down wherever we can. in fact, mrs. treves sometimes says that the only room she can call her own is the bedroom.}
<A>__{treves and anne laugh good naturedly. merrick's face, as always, is quite blank.}
<C>__{merrick}
<P>__{(earnestly)}
<D>__{well, it's a lovely bedroom. what do you call that thing above the bed?}
