<D>__{how is your tea, john?}
<C>__{merrick}
<D>__{it's very good. i'm enjoying my visit with you very much. it's so very kind of you to have me as a guest in your home. i'm sorry i made a spectacle of myself.}
<C>__{treves}
<D>__{not at all, john.}
<C>__{merrick}
<D>__{i love the way you've arranged your pictures on the mantlepiece. is that the way it's done in most houses?}
<C>__{treves}
<D>__{oh yes.}
<C>__{merrick}
<D>__{who are they of?}
